OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,FFraudulent CV-writing services are now
OL,7,Fthe biggest scamming threat to online
OL,8,Fjob hunters as the busy post-summer
OL,9,Fhiring season gets under way, LinkedIn
OL,10,Fhas warned.
OL,12,FThe professional networking site
OL,13,Frevealed that over a third (37%) of
OL,14,Fjob scams reported on the platform
OL,15,Fglobally now involve offers to write
OL,16,For improve CVs, which give poor
OL,17,Fquality or misleading results and
OL,18,Foften use artificial intelligence
OL,19,Ftools that are available at no cost.
