OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,FThese scams can also put personal
OL,7,Finformation at risk, with CV-writing
OL,8,Ffraudsters twice as likely to ask
OL,9,FLinkedIn members to take the
OL,10,Fconversation off the platform.
OL,12,FThe alert comes ahead of the typical
OL,13,Fannual jump in recruitment throughout
OL,14,FSeptember, with workers returning from
OL,15,Ftheir summer holidays and as new
OL,16,Fgraduates enter the workforce for the
OL,17,Ffirst time.
OL,19,FHiring soars by 44% on average in
OL,20,FSeptember across the UK, according to
OL,21,FLinkedIn.
