OL,6,FBut the group said there are now half
OL,7,Fas many job openings per applicant
OL,8,Fcompared with 2022, with recruitment
OL,9,Fbecoming ever more competitive.
OL,11,FOscar Rodriguez, vice president of
OL,12,Ftrust at LinkedIn, said: "Job hunting
OL,13,Fcan be a stressful time, which can
OL,14,Fleave people vulnerable, particularly
OL,15,Frecent graduates who are entering the
OL,16,Fjob market for the first time.
