OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,F"Scammers prey on anxiety and
OL,7,Finexperience, including offering
OL,8,Fservices that can compromise personal
OL,9,Fdata or cost money without delivering
OL,10,Fvalue.
OL,12,F"While the overwhelming majority of
OL,13,Ffake accounts on LinkedIn are blocked
OL,14,Fbefore they're reported, it's
OL,15,Fessential that job seekers stay
OL,16,Fvigilant and know what red flags to
OL,17,Flook out for so they can spot scams
OL,18,Fand stay safe in their job hunt."
