OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,FLinkedIn said it blocks 99.7% of fake
OL,7,Faccounts before they are reported, but
OL,8,Furged members to be vigilant and be on
OL,9,Falert to those offering these
OL,10,Fservices, with scammers five times as
OL,11,Flikely to come from outside a job
OL,12,Fseeker's network on the site.
OL,14,FRecent data has highlighted the
OL,15,Fworrying boom in recruitment fraud,
OL,16,Fwith Lloyds Banking Group revealing
OL,17,Flast month it had seen cases of
OL,18,F"advanced fee" job scams soar by 237%
OL,19,Fsince the start of this year.
