OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,FKeith Rosser, chair and company
OL,7,Fdirector at recruitment scam reporting
OL,8,Fservice JobsAware, said: "JobsAware
OL,9,Fhas witnessed a sharp increase in job
OL,10,Fscams over the last few years.
OL,12,F"Finding ways to make job searching
OL,13,Fsafer is crucial, especially as hiring
OL,14,Fbecomes more digital and scams become
OL,15,Fever more sophisticated."
