OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,F1. Scammers often use fake profiles
OL,7,Fwith little to no activity: Is this
OL,8,Fperson in your LinkedIn network? Do
OL,9,Fthey have a profile picture, followers
OL,10,Fand meaningful connections? Do they
OL,11,Fpost on their feed?
OL,13,F2. Scammers will try to take you away
OL,14,Ffrom the platform: Be cautious if you
OL,15,Fare asked to leave LinkedIn to visit
OL,16,Fanother website or continue the
OL,17,Fconversation elsewhere, including on a
OL,18,Fmessaging app.
