OL,3,CJob seekers at risk amid surge in CV-
OL,4,Cwriting scams, warns LinkedIn
OL,6,F3. Scammers will behave in suspicious
OL,7,For unprofessional ways: Unsolicited
OL,8,Fmessages, offers that seem too good to
OL,9,Fbe true, vague job descriptions, or
OL,10,Fpoor grammar and spelling can all be
OL,11,Fsigns of a scam.
OL,13,F4. Scammers may ask for your personal
OL,14,Finformation early on: A legitimate
OL,15,Forganisation will not ask for personal
OL,16,Fdetails like your National Insurance
OL,17,Fnumber, passport, or bank account
OL,18,Finformation in early conversations.
